---

<section id="tracks" class="section-dark">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="cinema-hero__title" style="text-align: center; font-size: 2.5rem;">ВЫБЕРИ СВОЙ ПУТЬ</h2>
        
        <div class="tracks-grid">
            <!-- Track 1: Actor -->
            <div class="track-card-cinema">
                <div class="track-card-cinema__bg">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1493612276216-9c5901955d43?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Actor" />
                </div>
                <div class="track-card-cinema__content">
                    <div class="track-card-cinema__badge">В кадре</div>
                    <h3 class="track-card-cinema__title">ACTOR</h3>
                    <p class="track-card-cinema__text">
                        Ты — лицо проекта. Учись работать на камеру, проходись по красной дорожке и получай главные роли.
                    </p>
                    <span class="track-card-cinema__link">
                        Стать актером →
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Track 2: Filmmaker -->
            <div class="track-card-cinema">
                <div class="track-card-cinema__bg">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579632652768-6cb9dcf85912?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80" alt="Filmmaker" />
                </div>
                <div class="track-card-cinema__content">
                    <div class="track-card-cinema__badge film">За кадром</div>
                    <h3 class="track-card-cinema__title">FILMMAKER</h3>
                    <p class="track-card-cinema__text">
                        Ты создаешь миры. Учись снимать, монтировать, писать сценарии и продюсировать контент.
                    </p>
                    <span class="track-card-cinema__link film">
                        Стать создателем →
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style lang="scss">
    // Local styles until moved to global SCSS
    .tracks-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 2rem;
        padding: 0 1rem;
        
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }
    }

    .track-card-cinema {
        position: relative;
        height: 500px;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: border-color 0.3s;

        &:hover {
            border-color: #FFD700;
        }

        &__bg {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-color: #111;
            
            img {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                object-fit: cover;
                opacity: 0.6;
                transition: opacity 0.3s;
            }
        }

        &:hover &__bg img {
            opacity: 0.4;
        }

        &__content {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            width: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, #000, transparent);
        }

        &__badge {
            background-color: #FFD700;
            color: #000;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 9999px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;

            &.film { background-color: #22d3ee; }
        }

        &__title {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #fff;
        }

        &__text {
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.5s;
        }

        &:hover &__text {
            max-height: 10rem;
        }

        &__link {
            color: #FFD700;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            
            &.film { color: #22d3ee; }
        }
    }
</style>
